data.name: label4.Text
data.value: This option enables setting language and regional options for the Administration Console and its plug-ins.

data.name: LblTBLoaderTimeout.ToolTip
data.value: The amount of inactivity time in minutes before the process closes itself (use -1 means that the process will never auto close itself)

data.name: LblDefaultWcfCallTimeout.ToolTip
data.value: The amount of time in minutes for WCF service calls not related to data transfer (such as CreateTB, CloseTB, etc.)

data.name: LblDefaultDataTransferWcfCall.Text
data.value: Timeout for data transfer WCF service calls (minutes)

data.name: LblDefaultDataTransferWcfCall.ToolTip
data.value: The amount of time in minutes for WCF service calls related to data transfer (such as SetData, GetData, etc.)

data.name: numericUpDown1.ToolTip
data.value: Maximum value of minutes after which the WMS CAL is considered purgeable because it is not working.

data.name: LblDBSizeMaxLevel.Text
data.value: Warn if database size exceeds this value (in GB)
